   screen);

b) Ensure the text described in (a) includes a functional hyperlink to the
   official CTRLD website (https://ctrld.io or the then-current official URL).
   The hyperlink must not use the rel="nofollow" attribute;

c) Not remove, obscure, or alter any existing copyright notices, attribution
   notices, or links to the CTRLD website contained in the Software;

d) Not misrepresent the origin of the Software or claim that You are the
   original author of the Software.

The Attribution requirement applies regardless of whether the Software is used
in its original form or as a Derivative Work.

